Documentation workflows fail when responsibilities are unclear and validation checkpoints are inconsistent.

## Structured approach

- Define mandatory documents per process stage
- Assign validation owners
- Track pending/missing items in one view
- Set escalation timing for critical cases

## Why this matters

In complex environments, documentation quality directly affects approval timelines, compliance, and execution reliability.

A disciplined workflow reduces rework and improves transparency across teams.
